 area code), date of birth, and email address on a 3 x 5 inch card, and mail it to “The Microsoft Rewards Ultimate Giveaway Sweepstakes, Free to Enter” at the address corresponding to your country of residence: For residents of the United States: P.O. Box 8554, Big Sandy, Texas, 75755-8554. For residents of Canada: c/o Helix Global Solutions Inc., 4612 Chemin Bois Franc, Saint Laurent, Quebec, H4S 1A7. For residents of the United Kingdom: c/o Bolloré, Thurrock Park Way, Tilbury, Essex, RM18 7HW, United Kingdom. For residents of France: c/o Bolloré, ZAC des Brateaux - Parc Euro Logistic, Bâtiment F porte A, Rue des 44 arpents, Villabe, 91100. For residents of Germany: c/o Bolloré Logistics Germany GmbH, Helix Global Solutions Inc., Obenhauptstrasse 11, 22335 Hamburg. Requests must be postmarked by 12/31/24 and received by 1/8/25. To enter and for Official Rules, including odds, and prize descriptions, visit [URL]. Void where prohibited. Canadian residents: Skill-testing question applies. Additional methods of entry into the Sweepstakes will be made available, see terms here. These additional methods are subject to the Official Rules  for the Sweepstakes including (but not limited to) any and all eligibility and registration requirements, as well as any limitation on the total number of entries which may be earned across all entry methods.</p>"},e.FDAuthProviderType={WindowsLive:"windows_live_id"},e.SessionCookieName="_uetsid",e.BingMobileAppCongratsQrcode="https://rewards.bing.com/rewardscdn/images/rewards/1Mhva/bing_mobile_app_congrats_qrcode.png",e.BingMobileAppCheckWinnerQrcode="https://rewards.bing.com/rewardscdn/images/rewards/1Mhva/bing_mobile_app_check_winner_qrcode.png",e.InstantWinSapphireLink="sapphirebing://miniApp?id=32649384730b2d61c9e79d46de589115&sa_source=2m_instant_win_landing&page=instantWin"}(e.Rewards||(e.Rewards={}))}(MeePortal||(MeePortal={}));__decorate=this&&this.__decorate||function(e,t,r,i){var n,s=arguments.length,a=s<3?t:null===i?i=Object.